{"tid":1668411,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"[NS] 牧場物語：重聚礦石鎮 #7 歡迎參加我同河童既婚禮","createTime":"2019-10-22T03:22:52.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-23T03:02:55.000Z","uid":34243,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"3f8a53514f5355fec4caff009fc78d84792441eb","tid":1668411,"uid":34243,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T03:22:52.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"http://asia.sega.com/bokumono/cht/img/top/keyvisual.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fasia.sega.com%2Fbokumono%2Fcht%2Fimg%2Ftop%2Fkeyvisual.png&h=24d9caf4&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>請盡量用不推文回覆</strong></span></div></span><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/awZjibO.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FawZjibO.jpg&h=48068a53&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xxH8VYu.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxxH8VYu.jpg&h=46f243c3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rSrtVYv.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrSrtVYv.jpg&h=6cb13fa0&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: purple;\"><ins>Q&amp;A</ins><br />\n1. 邊度拎魚竿？  身上留空位去海邊小屋<br />\n2. 點放低木石資材？ 家中左上櫃<br />\n3. 斧頭之類點拎？ 家中右下角櫃<br />\n4. 一開始點賺錢？ 種蘿蔔先啦，之後賽馬賺第一桶金，儲錢夏天種菠蘿<br />\n5.有無話點樣放羊同雞岀去？出面有個鈴 搖咗就會出黎 晚上八點會動物會自己跑翻入去<br />\n6.廚具點買？今集無咗電視購物，你第一次擴建間屋有廚房之後雜貨鋪老細過一排會寄信同你講有新廚具賣<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n其他重點：<br />\n1. 掘磺回體整咖喱烏龍麵，回60心，成本都係100蚊，全部都可以喺雜貨鋪買<br />\n<br />\n2. 詛咒工具解咒條件：<br />\n魚杆 斧頭: 用50次<br />\n錘仔 鐮刀: 連續裝備5日<br />\n水壺 鋤頭: 去教堂搵神父卸下詛咒工具5次 （教堂左邊間房，逢星期一、三 下午一點開）<br />\n<br />\n3. 今集無咗竹筐，轉咗加大背包</span></strong>"},{"pid":"00b29d1be312878103b526d68b990a3d8447b168","tid":1668411,"uid":34243,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"